These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, disaster, time-travel, western
City: paris, boston, marseilles, san-francisco
1. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person traveling to boston and the person watching disaster movies##2
4. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person watching disaster movies and the person watching animation movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | western         | disaster   | time-travel | animation       |
| City      | san-francisco | paris | marseilles   | boston |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, november, september, february
City: rome, nizza, miami, london
1. the person traveling to london is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person traveling to nizza##2
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Birthday         | november | december | september | february |
| City   | nizza    | london   | rome | miami       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, musician, police-officer, engineer
House: palace, townhouse, modern, art-deco
1. the modern house is on the right of the engineer##1
2. the modern house is between the townhouse house and the musician##2
3. the townhouse house is on the far left##1
4. the art-deco house is on the left of the police-officer##1
5. the musician is the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Job          | engineer    | dancer | musician   | police-officer  |
| House   | townhouse | modern   | art-deco | palace |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, documentary, comedy, scientific
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, bolivar, dunhill, game
1. the bolivar-smoker is the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the baccarat-smoker and the person watching scientific movies##2
3. the bolivar-smoker is on the far right##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre     | scientific   | martial-arts    | comedy       | documentary   |
| Cigar   | dunhill | game | baccarat | bolivar |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
4 different games are played: poker, backgammon, billiard, snooker
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, badminton, water-polo, golf
1. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far right##1
4. the person playing snooker is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's sport is badminton##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Game   | poker        | billiard | snooker  | backgammon |
| Sport      | water-polo | badminton  | golf | baseball    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, firefighter, social-worker, security-guard
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, taxi, bus, tram
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
2. the security-guard is the person driving the bus##1
3. the security-guard is on the far right##1
4. the firefighter is the person driving the van##1
5. the social-worker is between the photographer and the firefighter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Job   | firefighter     | social-worker           | photographer | security-guard  |
| Transport         | van | tram | taxi   | bus |

