.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, journalist, bartender, social-worker
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, soy-milk, almond-milk, tea
1. the journalist is the person drinking cola##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the librarian##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
5. the librarian is between the person drinking cola and the bartender##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Job   | social-worker   | journalist | librarian | bartender      |
| Beverage     | almond-milk | cola    | soy-milk  | tea |

