.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, august, march, february
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, zinnia, orchid, balloon-flower
1. the person who growsazalea is the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person who growszinnia is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who growsorchid##2
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1
4. the person who growsazalea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Birthday       | april | february | march     | august   |
| Flower   | orchid   | zinnia     | balloon-flower | azalea |

