House: farmhouse, craftsman, ranch-style, colonial
1. the person who growsrose is between the farmhouse house and the person who growsdaisy##2
2. the colonial house is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
4. the farmhouse house is on the left of the colonial house##1
5. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the ranch-style house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Flower         | lily | rose | daisy | dahlia |
| House   | farmhouse         | colonial       | craftsman    | ranch-style         |

