.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, blend, oliveros, game
City: paris, marseilles, london, colone
1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the game-smoker##1
2. the person traveling to london is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
3. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
4. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
5. the person traveling to marseilles is between the blend-smoker and the person traveling to colone##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Cigar    | game   | oliveros      | blend   | montecristo  |
| City   | colone | marseilles | london | paris |

