.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
City: nizza, edinburgh, prague, paris
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, metal, ambient, house
1. the fan house is on the right of the fan metal##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the person traveling to paris and the person traveling to nizza##2
3. the fan metal is on the right of the fan ambient##1
4. the fan ambient is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| City          | nizza     | edinburgh | paris   | prague        |
| Music-Genre   | funk | ambient   | metal | house |

