.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, biathlon, surfing, basketball
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, police-officer, entrepreneur, journalist
1. the entrepreneur is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the police-officer is on the left of the journalist##1
3. the mechanic is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is the police-officer##1
5. the mechanic is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
6. the police-officer is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's sport is basketball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Sport         | biathlon | surfing | basketball | water-polo |
| Job   | entrepreneur          | police-officer     | journalist  | mechanic     |

