2. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person who growspoppy and the person driving the motorbike##2
3. the person who growsbegonia is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Transport           | motorbike | snowmobile | van | car     |
| Flower   | tulip   | marigold    | poppy   | begonia |

