.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-14::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, bird, dog, guinea-pig
There 4 different types of food: papaya, broccoli, eggplant, lemon
1. the owner of the bird is the person eating eggplant##1
2. the person eating papaya is between the person eating lemon and the person eating broccoli##2
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the person eating lemon is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person eating eggplant is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Pet           | goldfish | guinea-pig | dog | bird |
| Food   | broccoli   | papaya | lemon         | eggplant |

