1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
3. the librarian is between the person who's birthday is in march and the software-developer##2
4. the electrician is the person who's birthday is in march##1
5. the journalist is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Job       | electrician | librarian | software-developer | journalist |
| Birthday   | march    | july  | november    | september       |

