.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, country, classical, jazz
There 4 different types of food: apricot, avocado, garlic, spinach
1. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
2. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
3. the fan jazz is the person eating apricot##1
4. the person eating spinach is between the fan techno and the fan classical##2
5. the fan classical is the person eating garlic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz   | techno   | country | classical |
| Food         | apricot | avocado | spinach     | garlic    |

