.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, lawyer, accountant, social-worker
4 different games are played: go, snooker, whist, mah-jongg
1. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
2. the writer is between the person playing go and the social-worker##2
3. the social-worker is on the left of the writer##1
4. the lawyer is on the far right##1
5. the lawyer is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Job   | accountant    | social-worker     | writer | lawyer |
| Game     | snooker | mah-jongg | whist       | go     |

 